snippet.title: Cadence of Hyrule: Crypt of the NecroDancer Ft. The Legend of Zelda - Nintendo E3 2019
snippet.description:
Play as Cadence, Link, or Princess Zelda as you move to the beat and try to defeat an evil menace disrupting Hyrule. Find out more about this title in the video above!

Follow Nintendo E3 coverage: http://e3.nintendo.com
